data.text:
Techron is a brand of fuel additives that are designed to clean and protect the engine and fuel system of vehicles. The brand offers a range of products that can be used with gasoline and diesel engines.

Techron was first introduced in the United States in 1954.

It was developed by the Chevron Corporation.

Over the years, Techron has evolved and improved to meet the changing needs of modern engines.

Today, Techron is a trusted brand used by motorists and mechanics around the world.

Brands Similar to Techron

Sea Foam

Sea Foam is a motor treatment that cleans and lubricates internal engine components. It is designed to eliminate varnish deposits and remove carbon buildup from engines.

Lucas Oil

Lucas Oil produces a range of additives and treatments for engines, transmissions, and other automotive systems. Its products are designed to clean, protect, and enhance the performance of vehicles.

BG Products

BG Products offers a range of oil and fuel additives that are designed to improve the performance and longevity of vehicle engines. Its products are used by mechanics and drivers around the world.
